Share with:
Sales Executive Job (Software and Services Solution Industry), Jakarta, Indonesia
Country:
Indonesia
Function:
Sales
Industry:
I.T.
Position type:
Permanent
Salary:
Negotiable
Created:
05 May 2014
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting on behalf of an established international information technology solutions provider. Our client offers provider of engineering and geospatial software that enables customers to visualize complex data. Businesses and governments in more than 60 countries rely on our client’s industry-specific software to organize vast amounts of data and infuse the world with intelligence to make processes and infrastructures better, safer, and smarter. The company’s software and services empower customers to build and operate more efficient plants and ships, create intelligent maps, and protect critical infrastructure and millions of people around the world. Our client is seeking a sales professional to fill the job of Sales Executive, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia.
Main responsibilities:
Direct and indirect sales of software and services solutions – primarily to the Energy, Resource and Marine & Offshore industries within the Indonesian market.
Main activities:
Expand Company’s solutions portfolio to existing accounts and develop new accounts in assigned territory and industry.
Ensuring that agreed business strategies are implemented.
Provide monthly sales report and participate in development of sales strategy.
Liaison with technical support team to provide optimum post-sales support to customers.
Liaison with Project Manager to ensure that projects are delivered on time and within budget.
Job requirements:
Experience in software solutions sales in Energy, Resources, and Marine & Offshore industries preferred.
Prior Channel and Direct sales experience advantageous.
The ability to thrive in a fast paced environment, and be entrepreneurial in nature.
Knowledgeable of Indonesian government procurement and tendering process
Able to travel within short notice
Behavioral Competencies:
Self-motivation and initiative
Positive interpersonal skills
Deadline driven
Planning & organization
Negotiation
Written & verbal communication (English and Bahasa Indonesia)
Teamwork
Accountability
Quality assurance/Attention to detail
All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence.